                <note rend="inline" type="source">825.00/673a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Culbertson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-08-01T12:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 1, 1931—noon</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>32. Your 84, July 28, 11 a.m. When will elections be called as provided in
                    Article 66 of the Constitution?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">White</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
